I have to get rid
of all this.

00:01:42.301 --> 00:01:43.703
It's impossible.

00:01:43.802 --> 00:01:45.839
I feel terrible
for Sal,

00:01:45.905 --> 00:01:47.474
but if
he had listened to me,

00:01:47.540 --> 00:01:50.043
